dc_description_s: These data layers represent recreational trails for Wood County, Wisconsin at year-end 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Wood_Trails_2017.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Wood_Recreation_Trails_2017' and 'Wood_Snowmobile_Trails_2017'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://opendata.woodcogis.com/
